%section#cats
  .container
    .divider
    .content
      .row-fluid
        .span12
          = image_tag image_path('cats-header.jpg')
      .row-fluid.grid-picture.cat
        .span3
          = image_tag image_path('strange.jpg')
        .span9
          %h3 Strange
          %p Strange is a three year old male white and black squeaky kitty. He may be getting older, but his kitten cry and sweet temperament makes him the baby of the group. He and Alastair love cuddling on the sofa and he will “eep” until you pick him up or feed him! He sulks when we run the vacuum and is convinced that the sofa will protect him from thunderstorms. His favorite things include feet, food, playing fetch with his toy mouse, and playing chase with his kitty brothers.
      .row-fluid.grid-picture.cat
        .span3
          = image_tag image_path('spin.jpg')
        .span9
          %h3 Spin
          %p Spin is our oldest kitty, but only by a few weeks. He is a three year old gray and silver tabby male domestic. He’s the man of the house and demands pet at all of the worst times. First thing in the morning and in the middle of the night are his favorites! He loves his Alastair though and will cry at the office until he comes out to pet him on his favorite bookshelf. His favorite things are perching on his cat tree, staring, boxes, playing with springs and bottlecaps, and being pet by his humans.
      .row-fluid.grid-picture.cat
        .span3
          = image_tag image_path('tau.jpg')
        .span9
          %h3 Tau
          %p Tau is the newest addition to our kitty family. We adopted Tau when he was one year old, however, he is a littermate to Strange. He and his brother get along best and will nap together regularly. Tau is a big turtle shell male domestic weighing in at about 25 pounds! He is by far the sweetest kitty of the three, likely because he is the simplest! He gets scared sometimes when he’s lost in the apartment, and screams when he’s separated from his kitty brother, but he doesn’t mind baths! Just hurry up before he gets tired and wants to lay down. His favorite things are food, sleep, feather toys, and food.
